data.description: Fantastic home in the heart of Livingston located in Davis Woods Subdivision!! A grand entry brings you into this superior quality custom built beautiful home offering an open concept split floorplan, 4BR 2.5BA 2car oversized garage, formal dining room, kitchen with custom cabinets, granite counters, stainless appliances & a breakfast area looking out on the back yard & pool. The living area is open to the kitchen, featuring a gas-log fireplace with  french-style doors out to the lovely back yard with a gorgeous inground pool!! The primary bedroom is large and has a small nook for a variety of uses. Another small bedroom is on this end of the home.  On the other end, the utility/laundry room is conveniently located just as you step in from the garage, and next are two bedrooms with "jack n jill" bathroom between. This is a lovely, peaceful neighborhood offering large trees, & underground utilities. Come see this home soon and make it yours. You will not be disappointed!!
